column5: I used to check OFC each day on the old board- until one day everyone was gone! Life is busy so until a couple days ago I noticed a reference to this board in a post on another board. It's good to be back. Enjoy the posts and pics.  >Bill
I think I know the board you are referring to, am a member there myself, but not under the same username.  Took ya long enough to find your way back
